<span foreground='Black' weight='bold' size='xx-large'>Phone Number</span>

The <b>Phone Number</b> of a <b>Contact</b> can be left blank, but when it is entered,
the input must look like it is a phone number.

For example, the following are <b>valid</b>:
(123) 456-7890
(123)-456-7890
+1 (123) 456-7890
+1-939 (123) 456-7890
123 456 7890
123 HEY HELO

And the following are <b>invalid</b>:
thisisaphonenumber
123 hello hello
1234567890
-1 (123) 456-7890
+1-1-939 (123) 456-7890
123 456 7890 home
